}¬} \par
\pard\tx520\tx1060\tx1600\tx2120\tx2660\tx3200\tx3720\tx4260\tx4800\tx5320\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 In this example, the Roland SC-7 sound module connects directly to the NeXT \i serial port\i0 , and also has a \i MIDI In\i0  socket for the connection of a keyboard controller.  The interface selection switch on the SC-7 must be set to RS-232C-1\f0\fs24 .\f0 \par
