\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Audio playback of music is controlled by means of the Playback Panel, which is displayed by pressing the menu command \fs24\f1\b0\i0 T\f1 ools\f2\f2 ®\f0  \fs24\f1\b0\i0 P\f1 erform:\f0 \par
